    "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/decision/cpb-cou1-accepted-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to level 1 per MRL 2 guidance and documented as not-assessed with adequate justification. The CFD hemolysis model for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in Class II CPB device submissions. The model may be used to support regulatory decision-making under the conditions described in the requirement and claim documentation. Overall credibility assessment: Accepted at Medium assurance level.",
